  "text": "BM-MSCs were a kind gift from Dr.Mohan Wani, NCCS (Pune). BM-MSCs were cultured in RPMI + 20 % Mesen FBS (GIBCO, Grand Island, NY, USA). Phenotypic characterization and differentiation to osteoblasts and adipocytes was carried out as explained earlier [CITATION_1] . Chondrogenic differentiation was carried out using a StemPro Chondrogenesis kit (Invitrogen, Grand Island, NY, USA) according to the manufacturer's instructions.",
